# Library Management System

A full-stack Library Management System built using Spring Boot, Thymeleaf, Spring Data JPA, and Oracle Database. The application helps manage books, students, book issuance, and returns through a user-friendly web interface.

## Features

* Add, update, delete, and view books
* Add, update, delete, and view students
* Issue books to students
* Return issued books
* Automatic book quantity management
* Track issue and return dates
* Responsive web interface using Bootstrap
* MVC architecture with Spring Boot

## Tech Stack

### Backend

* Java 17
* Spring Boot
* Spring Data JPA
* Hibernate

### Frontend

* Thymeleaf
* HTML5
* Bootstrap 5

### Database

* Oracle Database

### Build Tool

* Maven

---

